Name: Cat Capacity
About the game: Cats are forbidden in Rodentia, Baba disagrees. Developed by solo dev JT Mitchell. By King Uberlort's decree, cats are now illegal in Rodentia. Help Baba hide her beloved cats before Uberlort's goons catch her harboring a hoard of feline fugitives. If Baba is caught Uberlort's goons will throw her in the dungeon with yesterday's tuna. A hectic Katamari-inspired platformer/crazy cat lady sim, where you run around stuffing cats in closets while trolling Uberlort's dim-witted goons. -20 levels. -5 cat types. -2 modes. -2 enemy NPC types. -Dynamic point system. -Support Solo Dev JT Mitchell (Shameless plug).
